snippet.title: F1® 2018 | OFFICIAL GAMEPLAY TRAILER 2 | MAKE HEADLINES [US]
snippet.description:
Get closer to the real world sport with our brand new gameplay trailer for F1® 2018! Make Headlines in F1® 2018 - out 24th August.

Pre-order: http://bit.ly/F12018-Preorder

Find out more: http://bit.ly/F12018-Gameplay-Trailer-2
